<item>
            <title>[LU-2858] Attempts to delete .lustre/ should fail with EPERM</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2858</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On master, rm -rf $FSROOT/.lustre/ succeeds though it should (and used to) return EPERM.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to git bisect, the regression was introduced by change I7483b0f023e4e3de6597da58d3d9f3e96c0d53b7 (&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4339&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4339&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17686">LU-2858</key>
            <summary>Attempts to delete .lustre/ should fail with EPERM</summary>
